This paper is about the construction and evaluation of ensembles of artificial neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the subfield of machine learning. Specifically, the paper discusses algorithms for ensemble construction and their performance on standard statistical databases. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
